Package lame.std

Contains the symmetric Java elements of the standard LAME methods, structures and constants defined in the archive lame.h and exported in lame_enc.dll and libmp3lame.so/.dylib .

Contains the symmetric Java elements of the standard LAME methods, structures and constants defined in the archive lame.h and exported in lame_enc.dll and libmp3lame.so/.dylib .
